<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>I NEED THEE EVERY HOUR</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Phat chengin ka hun ngai,
 Zahngaihna Lal;
 Na Aw dam hieu banga,
 Ei lungmuon bei.

[V2]
 Ka hun ngai Aw ka hun ngai,
 Phat chengin ka hun ngai;
 Vang ei pie'n, tun Hukdampa,
 Ka hun zuon hi.

[V3]
 2. Phat chengin ka hun ngai,
 Ei umpih in;
 Thepna hatna a bei,
 Nang na naih tieng.

[V4]
 3. Phat chengin ka hun ngai,
 Nawp leh nat in;
 Hung mengin hung chengin,
 Hin phatchuom na'n.

[V5]
 4. Phat chengin ka hun ngai,
 Ei sinsak in;
 Na thutiem chu kei ah-
 Hih bukim in.

[V6]
 5. Phat chengin ka hun ngai,
 Mi thiengtho pen;
 Nanga ei hihsak in,
 Pathien Chapa.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>187</hymn_number>
</song>